px  -   pixel
        one onscreen pixel
        do not scale appropriately with device display density
        not recommended

dp  -   density-independent pixel (dip)
        1/160th of an inch on a device’s screen
        same size regardless of screen density
        recommended for layout dimensions, like margins, padding

sp  -   scale-independent pixel
        density-independent pixels that also take into account the user’s font size preference
        recommended for text size

pt   -  point
        1/72 of an inch
        not recommended

mm   -  millimeters
        not recommended

in   -  inch
        not recommended


Android will translate these values into pixels at runtime.
